apply to be a staff artist at the stanford daily arts at stanford university presented by sica home search this site arts enews subscribe for students opportunities apply to be a staff artist at the stanford daily deadline friday march 30 2012 paid like drawing or design or infographics the daily wants to pay you $8 per graphic email stnguyen stanford edu for an application working for the daily as a staff artist is a unique and challenging opportunity to expand your artistic skills in a flexible work environment a staff artist can expect to contribute 1 4 illustrations for the daily's articles on a weekly basis with opportunities to contribute to the weekly intermission and the annual big game coloring book issue illustrations range from depicting a snippet of news on campus to making informative graphs to accompany articles artists can simply send finished illustrations by email or stop by the office to upload them artists are given a biweekly salary of $8 per illustration people from all majors with any background in art or design in either a traditional or a digital medium are encouraged to apply contact stnguyen stanford edu for more info listed in job on campus see all opportunities prospective students check out the arts guide your multimedia guide to the arts at stanford stay updated student home events calendar opportunities in review subscribe curricular info majoring minoring creativity course guide arts intensive arts immersion arts circle make it happen money supplies space collaboration promotion beyond stanford internships career resources bay area arts back to arts at stanford make a gift volunteer login press sitemap contact connect twitter facebook vimeo flickr 2011 stanford university all rights reserved local user login
